Im Duk-yoon? Lee Jae-pyung?
Kuk Su-ran?

275
00:26:19,411 --> 00:26:20,673
Who the hell are you?

276
00:26:21,145 --> 00:26:22,374
Me?

277
00:26:22,580 --> 00:26:24,946
I'm sort of a scholar.

278
00:26:25,150 --> 00:26:27,641
And my major is you.

279
00:26:27,853 --> 00:26:30,013
A scholar studying Oh Dae-su.

280
00:26:30,221 --> 00:26:32,587
An expert on Oh Dae-su.

281
00:26:33,358 --> 00:26:34,586
Who I am isn't important.

282
00:26:34,792 --> 00:26:36,192
Why is important.

283
00:26:36,394 --> 00:26:37,919
Think it over.

284
00:26:38,230 --> 00:26:40,288
Review your whole lifetime.

285
00:26:41,267 --> 00:26:43,758
Since school is over,
it's time for your homework.

286
00:26:43,969 --> 00:26:45,128
Right?

287
00:26:46,872 --> 00:26:47,930
Keep this in mind.

288
00:26:49,307 --> 00:26:51,469
"Be it a grain of sand or rock,

289
00:26:52,344 --> 00:26:54,368
